        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2850378450" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15202445804757284073">I need to find the second book in this series and read it pronto....our library system has the first and the third, flipping typical that something good i&apos;d have to wait to find a way to get the second one. The characters are all good, the plot is really amazing. I kind of want to see exactly what they plan to do with the different worlds and everything. this book was seriously that good. Guess we&apos;ll have to see when I find the second book where the rest of the stuff goes! Till next time Echoes </span>
  <span id="freeText15202445804757284073" style="display:none">I need to find the second book in this series and read it pronto....our library system has the first and the third, flipping typical that something good i'd have to wait to find a way to get the second one. The characters are all good, the plot is really amazing. I kind of want to see exactly what they plan to do with the different worlds and everything. this book was seriously that good. Guess we'll have to see when I find the second book where the rest of the stuff goes! Till next time Echoes from the Edge series, I will totally come back for you!</span>
