        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer118402298" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8849330354380338216">This story gave me a lot of back and forth on how it made me first like it then unsure of whether I liked it at all as the book went on.<br/><br/>Interesting concepts but the execution fell short of what could have been something unique, if not quite so heavy on the ideas that Nathan kept his <i>purity</i> as taught by bits and pieces of parental advice.<br/><br/>I have second book also but not sure when I will read it, if ever.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


