        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3149138365" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4405772226401498796">I found the book pretty good. I enjoyed the narrative of saving the world and stuff. It was just as I got farther into it I started to feel like the author was preaching purity culture to me. Even as a Christian I felt pretty uncomfortable, especially since he was acting like the teen girl was unclean because of what might have happened in her past. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


